---

<Layout title="Win with Warranties - Day 41 Thrive">
    <Header />
    <main class="program-page">
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="gradient-overlay"></div>
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="animated-title">Win with Warranties</h1>
                <p class="hero-description">Elevating value and peace of mind</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="intro-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="intro-card">
                    <h2>Explore the Strategy</h2>
                    <p>At DAY 41 THRIVE, we help roofing contractors understand the true power of premium warranty programs and how they can transform your business. Selling industry-leading warranties is more than just an upsellâ€”it's a risk management tool, a credibility builder, and a competitive advantage.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="benefits-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Premium Warranties: A Transfer of Risk</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">Many roofing contractors offer workmanship warranties, but shouldering that risk alone can be costly. Premium manufacturer warranties change the game by shifting that liability away from your company.</p>
                
                <div class="benefits-grid">
                    {benefits.map(benefit => (
                        <div class="benefit-card">
                            <h3>{benefit.title}</h3>
                            <p>{benefit.description}</p>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>The Highest Quality Protection</h2>
                <div class="features-grid">
                    {gafFeatures.map(feature => (
                        <div class="feature-card">
                            <h3>{feature.title}</h3>
                            <p>{feature.description}</p>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="resources-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Contractor Programs & Resources</h2>
                <div class="resources-grid">
                    {resources.map(resource => (
                        <div class="resource-card">
                            <h3>{resource.title}</h3>
                            <p>{resource.description}</p>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="additional-benefits-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>More Than Just Rebates</h2>
                <div class="additional-benefits-grid">
                    {additionalBenefits.map(benefit => (
                        <div class="additional-benefit-card">
                            <h3>{benefit.title}</h3>
                            <p>{benefit.description}</p>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Ready to Protect Your Profits?</h2>
                <p>Transform your business with premium warranty programs. Let us show you how to maximize these powerful tools to build customer trust and secure your business.</p>
                <a href="mailto:hello@day41thrive.com" class="btn">Get Started Today</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <FloatingActionButton />
</Layout>

<style>
    .program-page {
        padding-top: 80px;
    }

    .hero {
        position: relative;
        background-image: url('/storm-bg.jpg');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        min-height: 50vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .gradient-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.95) 0%, rgba(255,20,147,0.3) 100%);
        z-index: 1;
    }

    .container {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    .animated-title {
        color: white;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero-description {
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.25rem);
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    section {
        padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    .intro-card {
        background: var(--card-bg);
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--primary);
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h2 {
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .section-intro {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 3rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .benefits-grid,
    .features-grid,
    .resources-grid,
    .additional-benefits-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .benefit-card,
    .feature-card,
    .resource-card,
    .additional-benefit-card {
        background: var(--card-bg);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--primary);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .benefit-card:hover,
    .feature-card:hover,
    .resource-card:hover,
    .additional-benefit-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    h3 {
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .cta-section {
        text-align: center;
        background: rgba(255, 20, 147, 0.05);
    }

    .cta-section p {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .benefits-grid,
        .features-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        }

        .resources-grid,
        .additional-benefits-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .benefits-grid,
        .features-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
        .intro-card,
        .benefit-card,
        .feature-card,
        .resource-card,
        .additional-benefit-card {
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>